text: Et his terminis hec terra cingetur.
Þanon on dæni swa northrihte to Petteleswige swa to Rithmærce.
Dicelinga & Stanmere & westmæstune swa eastrith to þan hwiten wæge swa north to wifelesfelde steton.
Swa east to mearchedige þanon est to mulestan.
To Wifeles felda ærest on Hæmpeles wyll.
And on frigedægæs east, swa to langan beccen.
Ðis is eastmærc to stanmere inn sinbl swa to humahamme eastweard to semænnes &langa hricge be landes mæbe into stanmere.
Swa north to heanfelde to wulfpytte.
Hec sunt nomina pastus porcorum. Qui pertinent ad stanmere.
Stealles felde northweard & citangaleahge wellinga stane.
And swa dæon on bære leage & on eastam on uuæsteat & hafocunga leahge.
